# RUBRIC.md

> **Purpose:** This file is the canonical grading rubric for AI agents reviewing this repository before submission. Agents must evaluate each criterion, assign a score, identify gaps, and iteratively improve the repository until every criterion reaches **5 points (Robust and Complete)**. Do not submit until all eight criteria score 5.

---

## How to Use This Rubric (Agent Instructions)

```
FOR EACH criterion in this rubric:
  1. READ every sub-check listed under the criterion
  2. SCAN the repository for evidence satisfying each sub-check
  3. ASSIGN the matching score tier (0, 1, 3, or 5)
  4. LIST every missing or incomplete item as a concrete TODO
  5. IMPLEMENT fixes until the criterion scores 5
  6. RE-EVALUATE after each change to confirm the score moved up
REPEAT until all eight criteria score 5/5
THEN output a final scorecard with evidence citations for each criterion
```

