## Criterion 4 — AI Maturity Scoring System

**What is being evaluated:** The AI maturity subsystem only. The four hiring signals are scored separately under Criterion 3.

### Sub-Checks (all must pass for 5 pts)

| ID | Sub-Check | Where to Look | Pass Condition |
|----|-----------|--------------|----------------|
| D1 | High-weight signals collected | `scoring/ai_maturity/` | Collection code for **AI-adjacent open roles** and **named AI/ML leadership** |
