Collection code for all six input categories (D1–D3). Scoring function returns integer 0–3 with per-signal justification (D4, D6). Weights match high/medium/low tiers (D5). Separate confidence field in output schema (D7). Silent company case handled explicitly (D8). Score rationale persisted alongside the brief (D9).

